{"tid":1226734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 而家要要求政府修訂其他法例送殺人犯去台灣先","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:03:05.000Z","uid":185502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6da8642ce38dcdd6f224e24e2d83de025f3be120","tid":1226734,"uid":185502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"既然林鄭認左逃犯條例引渡唔到台灣殺人犯<br />\n咁我地而家應該要剩勝追擊<br />\n要求政府修訂其他法例以確保今次台灣殺人案疑犯會被審訊<br />\n<br />\n林鄭一直以黎都用呢件事做藉口，咁要佢地修訂台灣都同意既法例黎處理呢件事，佢地都冇可能拒絕<br />\n<br />\n而修訂後，佢地都冇得再用類似既事黎做藉口重提修法"},{"pid":"d034b13a4836c4ad0ebef417b48921fb6f0e331a","tid":1226734,"uid":185502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0003dc0537eedd245ac0890c876d04e647ac0a51","tid":1226734,"uid":185502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}